{"name":"System Notes","pages":[{"sort":100000,"name":"Talents","type":"text","_id":"VJ0vXf42voEw3v3z","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"image":{},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p>This system ships items taken from Hackmaster Basic. You may use the following keys in an effect talent to replicate some talents from the full game, or to invent your own. Not every talent can be encoded into the game at this time, but support will grow as this system matures. Watch this space for more keys.</p><h2>Global Modifiers</h2><p>The following effect keys globally modify a character's stats. You should set the effect mode to Add for these. The system expects integer values here, except for top and move, which are floating point values (A move of 1.0 equates to a human's movement speed, and a top value of 0.1 would add 10% to that character's pain threshold).</p><pre><code>system.bonus.talent.atk\nsystem.bonus.talent.def\nsystem.bonus.talent.dmg\nsystem.bonus.talent.dodge\nsystem.bonus.talent.dr\nsystem.bonus.talent.foa\nsystem.bonus.talent.fos\nsystem.bonus.talent.hp\nsystem.bonus.talent.init\nsystem.bonus.talent.kb\nsystem.bonus.talent.mental\nsystem.bonus.talent.morale\nsystem.bonus.talent.move\nsystem.bonus.talent.physical\nsystem.bonus.talent.poison\nsystem.bonus.talent.reach\nsystem.bonus.talent.sp\nsystem.bonus.talent.spd\nsystem.bonus.talent.spdm\nsystem.bonus.talent.spdr\nsystem.bonus.talent.top\nsystem.bonus.talent.trauma\nsystem.bonus.talent.turning</code></pre>","markdown":""},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}},{"sort":0,"name":"Rulings","type":"text","_id":"9nF9I33L7c69uMMf","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"image":{},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p>This system follows Hackmaster, <em>Rules as Written</em>, whenever possible. While comprehensive, the game's realistic nature can lead to edge cases where no rule can tell a Game Master what to do and it became necessary for to make decisions on behalf of the Game Master. This journal documents these decisions so the Game Master and their Players are aware of them.</p><h2>Rules Priority</h2><p>Newer books supersede older books if their rules are contradictory. In increasing order of priority:</p><ul><li><p>Player's Handbook</p></li><li><p>Game Master's Guide</p></li></ul><p>This system also makes use of the <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1al7LYCJ497_8zLwFYwImk9mzbKXySrdzF0LPKSF5hFA/edit?usp=sharing\">Community Rules Errata</a>, which is maintained by the community. The errata contains game revisions made by the Official Hackmaster D-Team as well as some community decisions. Replies in green text are from the D-Team and treated as official. You are encouraged to review this document.</p><h2>System Rules</h2><p>The following decisions were made on behalf of Game Masters for the sake of automation:</p><p><strong>Half Damage Dice</strong></p><p>The procedure for halving a damage dice formula is as follows:</p><ol><li><p>Halve the number of dice (rounded down) for each term.</p></li><li><p>If a term's dice could not be halved (a singular die), then halve the number of faces, rounded down.</p></li></ol><h4><strong>Hurled Ranged Weapons with Negative Strength Damage Mod</strong></h4><p>Physically weak characters with damage penalties due to strength will receive their strength mod to non-mechanical ranged weapons. If a player indicates he has moved 10 feet/sec or faster, this strength penalty no longer applies.</p><h4><strong>Beast Attribute Bonus</strong></h4><p>Any time the rules refer to a player losing a bonus gained from attribute scores (which beasts lack), a penalty of -2 is applied to the beast, instead.</p>","markdown":""},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}}],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.xQmRPI8z1QssYNA8"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"hackmaster5e","systemVersion":"0","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1672582596240,"modifiedTime":1672642169549,"lastModifiedBy":"6PGvwKmaOsPz0R2y"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"6PGvwKmaOsPz0R2y":3},"_id":"IE2BBYp8sIMeUBUi"}
